{"tid":698224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請問呢一種係乜精神病？","createTime":"2018-06-11T13:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T14:05:00.000Z","uid":153892,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"619e27eec3becfb7565f546f729c15db3af46b2a","tid":698224,"uid":153892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:25:58.000Z","msg":"搭西鐵撞到個有問題既女人，首先我行埋去坐個陣唔小心踩到佢之後佢好似勁驚咁超大力踩返我，然後我無理坐落去，成程我聽緊歌無望佢但佢就成程用file遮住自己塊面，但隻手就係咁意輕輕咁撞我，之後到我差唔多落車個陣我忍唔住稍微啤一啤佢佢就勁串緊講咗兩句咩啊咩啊，然後就坐去我對面再用file遮住自己，到我落車之後我望一望佢又坐返原本個位。<br />\n<br />\n完全唔明發生咩事除咗一開頭唔小心踩到佢<br />\n<br />\n成程車都諗緊呢種係屬於邊種精神病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec69a9702f7d91d83239037f37faa445ee65ce8e","tid":698224,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"佢超大力踩返你個陣你當冇事?"},{"pid":"5117098d721d226e787e3cab8f5a90cd27611867","tid":698224,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ec69a9702f7d91d83239037f37faa445ee65ce8e","tid":698224,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"佢超大力踩返你個陣你當冇事?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:28:44.000Z","msg":"係,因為係我踩到佢先"},{"pid":"de66f24b2b0edf562fcf64793848055decda92e7","tid":698224,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec69a9702f7d91d83239037f37faa445ee65ce8e","tid":698224,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"佢超大力踩返你個陣你當冇事?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T13:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a61e85642541d78eb8f375c00943d8c355d02cf","tid":698224,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5117098d721d226e787e3cab8f5a90cd27611867","tid":698224,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ec69a9702f7d91d83239037f37faa445ee65ce8e","tid":698224,"uid":76098,"like"